<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="4850e641-425f-4aa2-a65a-9e9b77b184db" >

    <p>No, in fact it is an important first step towards equity and inclusion to know who is here and who isn't. If we don't know what the problems are, we can't fix them.</p>
    





</div>
