<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="6a637175-907b-4837-86e9-ea5743a10802" >

    <p>We still want and need to know who is here. Your answer definitely still matters to us because you are part of the Ryerson student body. We need the full picture to enhance the learning experience for all students.</p>
    





